<h2> Looking at the details of the game.</h2>
<p>Forza Horizon 4 was initially released on October 2, 2018, for Xbox One and PC, with early access starting September 28 for Ultimate Edition owners.
    The theme of Forza Horizon 4 is a dynamic, shared open-world automotive festival set in an idealized, changing Britain.Forza Horizon 4 was primarily developed by British studio Playground Games in collaboration with Turn 10 Studios.
</p>
